Package CAMs_App.controllers

Class CampComController

java.lang.Object
CAMs_App.controllers.UserController
CAMs_App.controllers.StudentController
CAMs_App.controllers.CampComController
public class CampComController extends StudentController
The StudentController class is responsible for handling the camp committee-specific user interface and user interactions. It extends the UserController class and provides functionality for committee memebers to view and reply to enquiries, create and edit suggestions, as well as generate reports.
